  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. Factual stub. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A \"mission control\" for LLM context: a DJ-style mixing board for the parameters you feed a model. Faders for context ratios, a memory graph, live token-window distribution, recipe presets for different personalities — all wrapped in a dense cyberpunk dashboard.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Context Alchemy — a DJ-style mixing board, memory graph, token distribution, and live system monitoring\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/context-alchemy/dashboard.png\" alt=\"Context Alchemy — a DJ-style mixing board, memory graph, token distribution, and live system monitoring\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/context-alchemy/dashboard.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/context-alchemy/dashboard.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/context-alchemy/dashboard.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/context-alchemy/dashboard.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Context Alchemy — a DJ-style mixing board, memory graph, token distribution, and live system monitoring\" width=\"1440\" height=\"4087\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.99deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1440×4087\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Context Alchemy — a DJ-style mixing board, memory graph, token distribution, and live system monitoring</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The mixing board up close — faders and knobs for every context parameter, an EQ spectrum, an analytical↔creative crossfader, and context-vinyl tur